WEBVTT

01:31.700 --> 01:35.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:35.980 --> 01:38.980
[Episode 24]

01:42.590 --> 01:43.820
Triple-flower mark?

01:52.840 --> 01:54.100
Li Jie's body

01:54.150 --> 01:56.120
was also transformed from the six-eyed butterfly.

01:56.120 --> 01:58.820
Its strength reached the triple-flower level long ago.

01:59.040 --> 02:01.100
But since he had no sacred power of his own,

02:01.680 --> 02:03.290
the flower mark never appeared.

02:04.000 --> 02:05.130
Now

02:05.150 --> 02:06.570
that my soul

02:06.640 --> 02:08.530
has fused with his body,

02:08.560 --> 02:10.490
the triple-flower mark

02:10.630 --> 02:12.060
naturally reveals itself.

02:13.150 --> 02:14.420
Well?

02:17.280 --> 02:19.210
Do you still think I'm insignificant now?

02:41.710 --> 02:42.490
Just as I thought.

02:43.910 --> 02:45.930
Looks like in all those rewinds,

02:46.030 --> 02:47.340
I never showed you

02:47.340 --> 02:48.530
the triple-flower mark.

02:49.150 --> 02:50.900
That's why you couldn't withstand my strike.

02:52.280 --> 02:53.530
Well?

02:55.030 --> 02:57.250
Do you still think you're a deity now?

02:59.150 --> 03:00.530
What destroys a deity

03:01.400 --> 03:02.530
is not a devil,

03:03.910 --> 03:06.140
but the deity's own arrogance.

03:09.870 --> 03:11.580
Your body has reached its limit.

03:13.080 --> 03:14.210
This is the last rewind.

03:20.960 --> 03:22.460
I fought so hard to get here.

03:23.960 --> 03:25.810
I won't allow myself to lose to you.

03:58.750 --> 04:00.020
This time,

04:01.310 --> 04:02.900
I will succeed.

04:32.120 --> 04:32.930
See?

04:37.040 --> 04:38.180
I succeeded.

04:39.870 --> 04:40.800
Do you know why

04:40.800 --> 04:42.180
I couldn't dodge your blade?

04:43.070 --> 04:45.180
Because I didn't want to.

04:48.310 --> 04:49.010
Break!

04:50.620 --> 04:52.660
♪It's your light, your storms...♪

04:53.830 --> 04:55.540
Dragon hearts as one,

04:56.000 --> 04:57.450
all to source return,

04:58.000 --> 04:59.570
all barriers break.

05:01.340 --> 05:05.380
♪Sailing afar♪

05:29.040 --> 05:29.780
It's raining!

05:38.510 --> 05:39.780
The drought is finally over.

05:40.160 --> 05:41.250
Luo'an is finally saved!

05:51.060 --> 05:57.460
♪Brewing the years into a daydream impossible to wake from...♪

05:57.680 --> 05:58.620
I did it.

06:05.100 --> 06:08.180
♪The white-haired one looks on through tear-blurred eyes...♪

06:09.750 --> 06:10.370
Wu.

06:13.430 --> 06:14.660
Ji.

06:20.310 --> 06:21.450
I did it.

06:31.680 --> 06:32.330
Wu?

07:24.300 --> 07:31.140
♪No pain, no tears, she takes it all in stride♪

07:31.660 --> 07:35.460
♪Facing the light, she's brave inside♪

07:35.900 --> 07:46.340
♪Who remembers dewdrops fade at dawn's light?♪

07:57.800 --> 07:58.620
This is for you.

08:05.950 --> 08:07.860
I'm sorry for staining

08:08.560 --> 08:09.130
your manuscript.

08:15.120 --> 08:15.860
Long,

08:16.190 --> 08:16.620
I...

08:18.120 --> 08:19.220
I promise I'll come back.

08:21.070 --> 08:21.490
Oh, right.

08:22.830 --> 08:23.620
I've asked

08:23.630 --> 08:24.930
my weasel brothers to look after you.

08:26.120 --> 08:27.130
If anyone dares hurt you,

08:27.560 --> 08:28.490
go ask them for help.

08:32.960 --> 08:34.730
I... I want to use this brush

08:35.080 --> 08:36.730
to write your story.

08:36.910 --> 08:38.090
When you come back next time,

08:38.150 --> 08:39.540
I'll... I'll let you read it.

08:42.080 --> 08:42.730
Do you like it?

08:45.360 --> 08:45.690
You...

08:46.150 --> 08:47.260
you didn't make this

08:47.440 --> 08:48.780
with your own fur, did you?

08:51.080 --> 08:51.730
Of course not.

08:53.460 --> 09:00.020
♪Up the hill, arms open wide, we sing♪

09:00.420 --> 09:06.780
♪You and me, we fear not a thing♪

09:08.220 --> 09:14.740
♪Life may sigh, but with our flesh and bone♪

09:15.180 --> 09:20.900
♪We brave the storm, and claim the truths we own♪

09:23.240 --> 09:24.730
I was the one

09:24.840 --> 09:26.780
who forced the rain to fall with demon magic.

09:27.550 --> 09:29.090
Why didn't I die?

09:32.840 --> 09:34.730
Some force even I do not know of

09:35.510 --> 09:36.500
was protecting you.

09:49.000 --> 09:49.810
But Ji Ling...

10:09.750 --> 10:11.540
People rarely get to have it both ways.

10:11.910 --> 10:13.260
He couldn't bear to let you die,

10:13.720 --> 10:15.330
but he also had to destroy Jiu Ying.

10:16.030 --> 10:17.020
Caught in that dilemma,

10:17.120 --> 10:18.380
he suffered deeply.

10:19.390 --> 10:20.900
You destroyed the Dragon Deity's Power

10:21.510 --> 10:23.030
and ruined the mission to which

10:23.030 --> 10:24.020
he'd devoted a century.

10:24.600 --> 10:25.380
And then he watched

10:25.380 --> 10:26.810
your body and spirit vanish.

10:27.670 --> 10:29.140
That overwhelming despair and loneliness

10:29.140 --> 10:30.180
snuffed out the last bit of hope

10:30.180 --> 10:31.540
in his heart.

10:32.790 --> 10:33.780
Thus,

10:34.630 --> 10:36.420
Lonescale consumed him.

10:37.790 --> 10:39.180
Lonescale lied to me.

10:40.240 --> 10:41.090
He said

10:41.550 --> 10:43.210
Ji Ling was a kind person.

10:43.510 --> 10:44.900
He said he chose to help me

10:45.270 --> 10:46.730
because he wanted to save Ji Ling too.

10:48.440 --> 10:50.180
I never thought it'd kill Ji Ling instead.

10:51.670 --> 10:52.660
You underestimated

10:52.660 --> 10:53.900
how much you meant to him.

10:56.080 --> 10:57.300
You wanted him to live

10:57.440 --> 10:58.300
and yourself to die.

10:59.030 --> 11:00.260
He wanted the opposite.

11:01.270 --> 11:02.810
Lonescale can rewind time

11:02.910 --> 11:04.850
and peer into the past and future.

11:05.440 --> 11:07.180
How could he not have known how it would end?

11:07.750 --> 11:09.210
He knew everything all along,

11:09.840 --> 11:11.260
and that was exactly why he chose to help you.

11:12.240 --> 11:13.420
From beginning to end,

11:13.840 --> 11:15.180
he had only one goal:

11:16.510 --> 11:18.060
to consume Ji Ling completely.

11:22.080 --> 11:24.140
I ruined your plan.

11:25.320 --> 11:27.140
You spent over 100 years playing the Dragon Deity,

11:28.000 --> 11:28.780
alone

11:29.750 --> 11:30.500
and in pain,

11:32.550 --> 11:34.690
all just so you could reach that very ending.

11:36.720 --> 11:38.450
But I couldn't stand by and watch you die.

11:39.840 --> 11:42.020
You shouldn't have existed in this world

11:42.750 --> 11:44.180
just to sacrifice yourself.

11:46.240 --> 11:47.660
That would've been too cruel to you.

11:51.550 --> 11:52.500
I never thought

11:55.960 --> 11:57.570
it would turn out like this.

12:06.750 --> 12:07.450
Ji Ling,

12:09.910 --> 12:11.500
can you hear me?

12:12.910 --> 12:14.260
Please wake up.

12:22.870 --> 12:24.090
Back then, I didn't understand

12:26.440 --> 12:27.810
why so many demons wanted

12:29.720 --> 12:30.660
to wear

12:31.870 --> 12:32.850
human skin

12:35.150 --> 12:36.260
and become human.

12:38.270 --> 12:39.570
A demon's tears

12:40.150 --> 12:41.260
are fake.

12:43.240 --> 12:44.930
They cry just to look

12:44.930 --> 12:46.180
more human.

12:47.750 --> 12:48.930
I don't understand

12:49.870 --> 12:50.850
why so many demons

12:51.720 --> 12:52.500
want to wear

12:53.270 --> 12:54.300
human skin

12:55.670 --> 12:57.060
and become human.

12:58.120 --> 12:59.570
But now I do.

13:10.750 --> 13:12.500
I want to be with you

13:15.000 --> 13:16.610
and live as the most ordinary of people,

13:18.910 --> 13:20.180
beginning work at sunrise

13:21.390 --> 13:22.850
and resting at sunset,

13:24.320 --> 13:25.450
walking hand in hand

13:26.630 --> 13:28.020
through the streets,

13:31.440 --> 13:32.610
and falling asleep

13:33.600 --> 13:35.020
in each other's arms at night.

13:53.390 --> 13:54.850
Ji Ling has been consumed by Lonescale

13:55.240 --> 13:56.260
and remains unconscious.

13:57.030 --> 13:59.020
Bai Ze told us to go to Chi Wen in the Dragon Abyss.

13:59.600 --> 14:01.330
He may have a way to save him.

14:03.200 --> 14:05.420
But without the last share of the Dragon Deity's Power,

14:05.790 --> 14:06.660
I can't become a dragon.

14:07.790 --> 14:09.090
When I get there,

14:09.670 --> 14:11.690
I don't know how I'll face my brother.

14:20.750 --> 14:22.090
Whether you become a dragon or not,

14:22.480 --> 14:23.450
you are still you,

14:25.600 --> 14:26.540
Wu Shiguang.

14:30.840 --> 14:33.420
You taught me in the Star Stone illusion

14:33.870 --> 14:35.020
that who we are

14:36.320 --> 14:38.690
has nothing to do with background or bloodline.

14:39.440 --> 14:41.020
What matters more is whom we love

14:41.790 --> 14:43.060
and what we choose to protect.

14:45.240 --> 14:46.090
Besides,

14:46.550 --> 14:47.810
fortune and misfortune go hand in hand.

14:48.320 --> 14:50.260
Without the last share of the Dragon Deity's Power,

14:50.720 --> 14:52.570
you will no longer be able to kill Chi Wen,

14:53.150 --> 14:54.020
and Jiu Ying

14:54.870 --> 14:55.960
will stop trying

14:55.960 --> 14:57.090
to possess you.

14:59.440 --> 15:00.690
But if I can't become a dragon,

15:01.790 --> 15:03.090
I can't destroy the Oracle Stone.

15:04.200 --> 15:05.500
When the next full moon comes,

15:05.720 --> 15:07.380
you'll be forced back to the Formless Moon.

15:07.510 --> 15:08.060
I'm afraid...

15:08.440 --> 15:09.260
It's all right.

15:10.270 --> 15:11.330
There's still time.

15:13.910 --> 15:14.730
Besides,

15:16.550 --> 15:17.780
I can sever my tail.

15:23.840 --> 15:25.060
That's the worst possible choice.

15:25.240 --> 15:26.060
No, it isn't.

15:28.600 --> 15:30.060
I'm not like Xiaowei.

15:32.790 --> 15:34.180
I still have you.

15:47.600 --> 15:48.450
What do you

15:49.080 --> 15:50.330
think of this color?

15:56.790 --> 15:57.540
What do you think?

16:02.510 --> 16:04.180
Mortal couples bind strands of their hair together.

16:05.840 --> 16:06.570
At first,

16:07.600 --> 16:09.060
I didn't understand what it meant.

16:10.120 --> 16:11.260
I only wanted a good omen.

16:12.910 --> 16:14.660
But when I braided your hair together

16:14.840 --> 16:15.780
with mine,

16:16.840 --> 16:17.570
I realized

16:18.270 --> 16:19.500
that once hair strands are entwined,

16:20.320 --> 16:21.260
unless they break,

16:22.270 --> 16:22.970
they are

16:24.670 --> 16:25.780
almost impossible to part.

16:27.030 --> 16:27.970
You and I are the same.

16:29.550 --> 16:31.060
We were fated to be entangled long ago.

16:33.240 --> 16:34.810
I will protect you no matter what

16:36.360 --> 16:38.090
and never fail this vow sealed by our bound hair.

17:29.160 --> 17:30.220
You lied to me.

17:35.480 --> 17:36.700
I didn't.

17:37.720 --> 17:38.980
I truly hoped

17:39.550 --> 17:40.610
you'd be able to save him.

17:42.030 --> 17:44.130
What nurtured that dragon scale into a demon

17:45.350 --> 17:47.170
was not only his loneliness

17:48.270 --> 17:49.780
but also his kindness.

17:50.750 --> 17:52.220
Then take me back again.

17:53.200 --> 17:54.130
I want to save him.

18:01.550 --> 18:02.330
It's useless.

18:04.160 --> 18:05.330
He remains unconscious

18:05.960 --> 18:07.460
because his consciousness

18:08.110 --> 18:09.500
has returned to the past.

18:10.880 --> 18:12.170
He's trapped in that part of his past

18:12.240 --> 18:13.610
that came to haunt him.

18:16.590 --> 18:18.300
Haunt him?

18:19.720 --> 18:21.370
It's the old days

18:21.370 --> 18:22.540
before I was born.

18:34.640 --> 18:35.850
Then take me there.

18:37.200 --> 18:38.650
No matter how far back it is,

18:39.880 --> 18:40.940
I'm not afraid.

18:42.590 --> 18:43.650
I can take it.

18:47.960 --> 18:49.500
I know you can.

18:51.720 --> 18:53.220
And I can take you there

18:53.960 --> 18:55.300
so you can see

18:55.960 --> 18:57.740
why he became so lonely.

18:59.750 --> 19:00.500
But...

19:02.030 --> 19:02.780
But what?

19:05.030 --> 19:06.410
But that was

19:06.830 --> 19:08.650
more than 100 years ago.

19:09.750 --> 19:10.980
Far too long ago.

19:12.000 --> 19:14.260
No power can change it.

19:15.270 --> 19:15.890
So

19:16.240 --> 19:17.780
you won't be able to rewind time

19:18.350 --> 19:20.060
again and again like you did before

19:20.680 --> 19:21.780
to alter the past.

19:22.720 --> 19:23.300
Besides,

19:24.160 --> 19:24.890
you

19:25.640 --> 19:26.170
did not

19:27.960 --> 19:28.940
exist there.

19:30.790 --> 19:31.890
Back then,

19:32.240 --> 19:33.330
there was no Lu Wuyi

19:33.790 --> 19:34.850
by Ji Ling's side.

19:35.510 --> 19:36.570
You can only be

19:36.570 --> 19:37.980
a silent observer,

19:38.680 --> 19:40.410
unable to interfere in any way.

19:43.160 --> 19:44.300
Do you still want to go?

19:47.020 --> 19:49.500
♪Don't be sad♪

19:49.500 --> 19:51.220
♪Through every yesterday...♪

19:51.790 --> 19:52.810
This story

19:53.920 --> 19:54.980
is far too long.

19:56.030 --> 19:57.460
Even a day and a night wouldn't be enough.

19:58.310 --> 19:59.540
When we return from Luo'an,

20:00.400 --> 20:01.570
I'll tell it to you slowly.

20:04.380 --> 20:06.940
♪Don't be sad♪

20:06.980 --> 20:08.660
♪Through every lonely night♪

20:08.740 --> 20:11.180
♪Don't you cry♪

20:11.260 --> 20:13.060
♪Through the darkest nights...♪

20:13.440 --> 20:13.980
I do.

20:19.200 --> 20:20.090
I want to know

20:22.960 --> 20:23.980
his past.

20:24.460 --> 20:26.100
♪Through a thousand broken lights♪

20:26.180 --> 20:28.780
♪Don't you cry♪

20:28.780 --> 20:30.380
♪Through every love and every pain♪

20:30.500 --> 20:36.020
♪I'll always stay with you♪

20:36.740 --> 20:38.620
♪Stay with you♪

20:59.510 --> 21:00.130
Yuan Xizai!

21:20.980 --> 21:24.180
[A hundred and fifty years ago]

22:06.550 --> 22:07.170
Xizai.

22:10.110 --> 22:10.880
Xizai?

22:11.750 --> 22:12.520
Xizai!

22:13.280 --> 22:14.130
Xizai.

22:15.440 --> 22:16.020
Xizai!

22:18.030 --> 22:18.610
Save him.

22:19.720 --> 22:20.410
Quick, save him!

22:22.270 --> 22:22.980
Save him!

22:23.020 --> 22:25.220
♪Trapped in this body...♪

22:25.790 --> 22:26.500
Where's your magic?

22:27.590 --> 22:28.540
Why don't you have any magic?

22:29.880 --> 22:30.810
Hurry up and heal him.

22:32.960 --> 22:33.500
Do it!

22:33.920 --> 22:34.500
Hurry!

22:34.640 --> 22:35.410
Save him!

22:36.790 --> 22:37.540
Save him!

22:39.960 --> 22:40.540
Wuhuo...

22:42.220 --> 22:44.660
♪They laugh at me for going mad♪

22:45.100 --> 22:47.900
♪So what if I have?♪

22:48.540 --> 22:51.500
♪Miss me not, miss me not♪

22:51.700 --> 22:54.700
♪When heavy snow falls on the frozen river♪

22:54.900 --> 22:57.260
♪Even the wind will say♪

22:57.660 --> 23:01.540
♪It was never here♪

23:03.460 --> 23:06.660
♪Just lend me one more tomorrow♪

23:06.900 --> 23:09.700
♪To go and see places farther away♪

23:10.140 --> 23:12.860
♪I am not afraid of having no one and no shore♪

23:13.020 --> 23:15.900
♪It is what I willingly choose♪

23:16.380 --> 23:19.180
♪I only need to wipe my tears dry♪

23:19.380 --> 23:22.540
♪No matter how small I am, I can still be brave...♪

23:28.590 --> 23:29.650
Save my brother,

23:30.310 --> 23:31.410
and I'll let you go.

23:36.460 --> 23:42.580
♪Then sink into a sleep as still as jade♪

23:45.400 --> 23:46.890
It's almost New Year's Eve.

23:47.510 --> 23:49.370
Everyone, sort through your things and throw out

23:49.510 --> 23:50.700
what you don't need.

23:51.240 --> 23:52.500
Sweep away the dust and grime,

23:52.880 --> 23:55.300
say goodbye to the old, and welcome the new!

23:55.750 --> 23:56.960
I don't want to see you

23:56.960 --> 23:58.650
live your whole life timid and weak,

23:58.960 --> 24:00.020
bullied by others.

24:00.510 --> 24:02.090
Take the Dragon Marrow

24:02.400 --> 24:03.650
and become

24:04.200 --> 24:05.570
a demon hunter like me.

24:06.270 --> 24:08.300
But I don't want to be a demon hunter.

24:08.920 --> 24:10.850
I'm... I'm afraid of demons.

24:15.960 --> 24:16.540
Commander Yuan.

24:16.540 --> 24:19.070
[Ye Daoxuan, attendant]

24:19.070 --> 24:20.700
These were all Xizai's belongings.

24:21.830 --> 24:22.540
Throw them away.

24:24.550 --> 24:25.060
All right.

24:25.720 --> 24:26.890
That might be for the best.

24:33.940 --> 24:37.540
♪As another year comes around, every home is busy getting ready♪

24:37.700 --> 24:40.860
♪Fireworks bloom in the sky♪

24:41.660 --> 24:48.340
♪We softly hum tunes while sweeping every corner♪

24:49.980 --> 24:53.500
♪Window paper-cuts bring peace and joy...♪

24:57.110 --> 24:57.940
Master Daoxuan.

24:59.500 --> 25:04.140
♪May the new year be free of disaster and misfortune♪

25:05.300 --> 25:11.860
♪Fireworks sparkle like stars falling into our eyes♪

25:13.140 --> 25:19.940
♪Snow hangs from the eaves, waiting for swallows to bring back spring♪

25:21.180 --> 25:25.500
♪Another year goes by, and little by little♪

25:25.500 --> 25:28.740
♪Those who've left home have wandered far away♪

25:28.940 --> 25:30.700
♪If only we could go back♪

25:31.180 --> 25:32.620
♪Back to childhood♪

25:33.100 --> 25:36.900
♪Back to the joy that felt whole♪

25:45.440 --> 25:46.330
The New Year's coming.

25:47.160 --> 25:48.330
I've brought you something delicious.

25:49.880 --> 25:51.260
Maybe it'll help you

25:53.350 --> 25:54.740
recover your powers.

26:00.510 --> 26:01.890
Why do you have it?

26:03.400 --> 26:04.170
Let go.

26:04.680 --> 26:05.850
This isn't yours.

26:08.270 --> 26:09.410
It was all your fault.

26:12.160 --> 26:13.850
You wouldn't save my brother,

26:15.160 --> 26:17.130
so he died.

26:18.390 --> 26:19.260
Why?

26:20.030 --> 26:21.130
Why wouldn't you save him?

26:22.680 --> 26:24.060
Since you wouldn't save him,

26:26.590 --> 26:27.850
you can die too!

27:31.020 --> 27:32.580
♪One winter day♪

27:33.580 --> 27:37.740
♪By the lake, a boy in white opened his eyes...♪

27:39.750 --> 27:40.500
Wuhuo,

27:41.640 --> 27:42.940
I'm afraid of demons.

27:50.350 --> 27:52.090
What... what kind of demon trick is this?

27:53.400 --> 27:54.370
I didn't do anything.

27:56.070 --> 27:57.500
I don't know any demon tricks.

28:02.070 --> 28:03.740
Did you think that if you took this form,

28:04.270 --> 28:05.810
I wouldn't have the heart to kill you?

28:18.000 --> 28:18.460
Wuhuo!

28:18.590 --> 28:19.090
Take it.

28:19.750 --> 28:20.300
Swallow it!

28:20.300 --> 28:21.020
No!

28:21.350 --> 28:22.090
Swallow it!

28:23.340 --> 28:29.980
♪How deep is the abyss? How heavy is the vow?♪

28:30.420 --> 28:32.740
♪A regret no repentance can erase♪

28:32.820 --> 28:36.780
♪Pressing against an aching heart♪

28:37.380 --> 28:44.740
♪Through countless trials and lifetimes, each of our souls...♪

28:46.880 --> 28:47.780
Give one to Xizai too.

28:47.960 --> 28:48.540
Here.

28:48.750 --> 28:50.020
I've already eaten, Wuhuo.

28:50.110 --> 28:51.020
I don't care.

28:52.000 --> 28:53.260
Mother made them.

28:53.680 --> 28:54.260
Here. Eat one.

28:54.510 --> 28:55.540
I've eaten.

28:55.830 --> 28:56.610
Look how thin you are.

28:56.880 --> 28:57.540
Eat more.

28:57.790 --> 28:58.540
Go on. Eat.

28:59.070 --> 28:59.890
Eat more.

29:00.440 --> 29:01.170
Grow stronger,

29:01.440 --> 29:02.170
just like your brother.

29:04.960 --> 29:05.810
Wuhuo, you're amazing.

29:12.640 --> 29:13.220
Commander Yuan,

29:14.240 --> 29:14.850
I found it.

29:15.960 --> 29:17.570
It turns out the first skin a demon wears

29:17.590 --> 29:18.540
to take human form

29:18.880 --> 29:20.570
uses blood as its medium.

29:23.590 --> 29:24.460
If its blood

29:24.960 --> 29:25.890
stains an object

29:26.480 --> 29:28.090
laden with intense emotion,

29:29.000 --> 29:29.850
the demon

29:29.920 --> 29:31.460
will naturally take on the appearance

29:32.200 --> 29:33.500
of that object's owner.

29:42.790 --> 29:43.460
Commander Yuan,

29:44.960 --> 29:46.330
I thought you were looking up

29:46.350 --> 29:47.740
remedies for the Wasting Sickness.

29:49.030 --> 29:49.980
Turns out it was this.

29:54.880 --> 29:55.700
How have you

29:56.110 --> 29:57.060
been feeling lately?

29:58.070 --> 29:59.570
Who would've thought the Meteor Blast

30:00.000 --> 30:01.410
would cause the Wasting Sickness?

30:05.660 --> 30:12.660
♪Has anyone heard my call?♪

30:16.110 --> 30:17.090
I'm human now.

30:17.090 --> 30:18.780
It's so inconvenient not having claws.

30:19.680 --> 30:21.060
I can't even leave marks.

30:25.700 --> 30:31.660
♪A speck of dust weighs heavy on my heart and throat♪

30:32.540 --> 30:39.580
♪I pace back and forth, counting footprints, too afraid to look up♪

30:39.700 --> 30:46.020
♪Trapped like rainwater in a lake♪

30:46.640 --> 30:47.330
Thank you.

31:08.830 --> 31:10.330
Why do you sound

31:10.830 --> 31:12.090
like you're crying?

31:14.030 --> 31:14.540
Are...

31:15.680 --> 31:17.330
are you sad?

31:20.000 --> 31:21.850
I don't know whether I'm sad

31:25.640 --> 31:26.890
or happy.

31:31.960 --> 31:33.780
I... I think I understand.

31:36.110 --> 31:39.090
Did I become someone

31:41.200 --> 31:42.300
you knew?

31:45.590 --> 31:46.410
Was that person

31:47.720 --> 31:48.980
very important to you?

31:53.240 --> 31:54.130
Father, Mother!

31:59.160 --> 31:59.610
Father!

32:00.550 --> 32:00.980
Father?

32:02.550 --> 32:02.980
Mother...

32:03.350 --> 32:04.260
Wuhuo,

32:06.240 --> 32:07.460
it was the wolf demons.

32:08.440 --> 32:10.650
Take care of your little brother.

32:16.400 --> 32:17.030
And...

32:19.350 --> 32:20.850
don't tell him the truth.

32:21.720 --> 32:24.130
Xizai is timid.

32:30.550 --> 32:31.090
Wuhuo,

32:31.680 --> 32:34.460
why does it smell so strongly of blood?

32:36.920 --> 32:38.300
It was rare for me to come home,

32:39.270 --> 32:40.940
so Father caught two wild chickens

32:41.750 --> 32:44.090
and stewed them for me.

32:44.920 --> 32:46.500
Father, Mother, and I talked it over.

32:48.590 --> 32:50.060
You should take the Dragon Marrow

32:51.440 --> 32:52.540
and become

32:53.200 --> 32:54.370
a demon hunter like me.

32:54.370 --> 32:55.020
No!

32:56.350 --> 32:57.170
Father and Mother

32:57.170 --> 32:58.130
would never agree to it!

32:58.830 --> 33:00.020
Even healthy, strong people

33:00.110 --> 33:01.130
often die

33:01.160 --> 33:02.460
after swallowing Dragon Marrow.

33:02.830 --> 33:03.300
Wuhuo,

33:04.880 --> 33:05.940
I'll die!

33:06.160 --> 33:07.500
Those were greedy fools

33:08.000 --> 33:09.170
who swallowed it recklessly

33:09.200 --> 33:10.260
just to gain sacred power.

33:10.920 --> 33:12.850
The Shilin Sect tested my constitution.

33:13.480 --> 33:14.570
You're like me.

33:16.880 --> 33:17.810
You'll be fine.

33:18.200 --> 33:19.810
But I don't want to be a demon hunter.

33:21.790 --> 33:23.060
I'm afraid of demons.

33:23.060 --> 33:24.060
If you're this cowardly,

33:24.720 --> 33:26.300
how will you survive in this chaotic world?

33:28.790 --> 33:30.570
I never wanted to survive.

33:32.240 --> 33:34.330
I've already dragged our family down.

33:35.880 --> 33:36.410
Wuhuo,

33:40.070 --> 33:41.460
just let me die.

33:45.160 --> 33:45.890
All right?

34:08.630 --> 34:09.540
No need to be scared.

34:11.230 --> 34:13.020
They're firecrackers we set off to celebrate

34:13.440 --> 34:14.290
New Year's Eve.

34:16.030 --> 34:16.690
What is

34:17.670 --> 34:18.500
New Year's Eve?

34:21.920 --> 34:22.900
New Year's Eve...

34:26.070 --> 34:27.540
Xizai, do you hear that?

34:27.760 --> 34:29.900
They're setting off firecrackers and doing the dragon dance.

34:31.840 --> 34:32.500
I hear it.

34:32.580 --> 34:38.060
♪We softly hum tunes while sweeping every corner..♪

34:38.070 --> 34:38.730
Look.

34:39.550 --> 34:40.650
How lively it is.

34:40.900 --> 34:44.420
♪Window paper-cuts bring peace and joy...♪

34:48.550 --> 34:49.900
Father, Mother!

34:50.150 --> 34:51.250
Your brother is here.

34:51.320 --> 34:51.820
Wuhuo.

34:51.920 --> 34:53.030
- Father, Mother. - You're here, Wuhuo.

34:53.550 --> 34:54.570
You've grown sturdier.

34:55.230 --> 34:56.380
We missed you.

34:56.380 --> 34:57.130
I missed you too.

34:59.110 --> 34:59.610
Xizai,

34:59.670 --> 35:00.650
you've gotten so tall.

35:01.400 --> 35:02.570
Your mother made dumplings.

35:02.570 --> 35:03.690
Mother made dumplings?

35:03.800 --> 35:04.170
Here.

35:04.290 --> 35:05.820
- Try it. - Eat, Wuhuo.

35:06.000 --> 35:06.980
They're still hot.

35:09.840 --> 35:10.420
Delicious.

35:10.420 --> 35:11.020
You like it?

35:11.840 --> 35:12.690
Give one to Xizai too.

35:13.190 --> 35:14.420
I've already eaten, Wuhuo.

35:14.550 --> 35:15.340
I don't care.

35:15.580 --> 35:16.670
- You're too thin. - I've eaten.

35:16.710 --> 35:17.210
Here.

35:17.670 --> 35:18.210
Eat one.

35:18.550 --> 35:19.380
Go on. Eat.

35:19.860 --> 35:21.620
♪If only we could go back♪

35:22.100 --> 35:23.540
♪Back to childhood♪

35:24.020 --> 35:26.540
♪Back to the joy that felt whole♪

35:26.550 --> 35:27.420
There's plenty more.

35:28.360 --> 35:29.820
New Year's Eve

35:30.710 --> 35:31.860
is the most beautiful

35:33.320 --> 35:34.820
and happiest day in the human world.

35:44.220 --> 35:48.300
♪Who still remembers♪

35:48.780 --> 35:51.820
♪The child I used to be?♪

35:52.260 --> 35:54.020
♪Under the sparks of fireworks♪

35:54.260 --> 35:55.940
♪I gently clasped my hands♪

35:56.260 --> 36:00.980
♪Wishing for a life free of harm♪

36:01.000 --> 36:01.820
Is this for me?

36:03.590 --> 36:04.170
It is.

36:05.360 --> 36:05.940
Eat.

36:07.670 --> 36:08.860
May you be free of misfortune

36:09.960 --> 36:11.210
in the coming year.

36:51.280 --> 36:51.980
Here.

36:52.230 --> 36:53.020
You eat some too.

36:56.920 --> 36:58.460
I've gotten grease all over your hands.

36:59.190 --> 36:59.650
It's all right.

37:00.000 --> 37:01.090
I'll wash them for you.

37:35.920 --> 37:36.650
You're

37:36.960 --> 37:38.290
a little fox.

37:38.920 --> 37:40.130
How can you not have fur?

37:42.150 --> 37:43.090
A bald fox

37:43.320 --> 37:44.860
will get laughed at.

37:45.670 --> 37:47.690
But my eyes can't see,

37:48.760 --> 37:49.610
so I don't know

37:50.150 --> 37:51.770
if I've dressed you up nicely.

37:53.400 --> 37:54.940
As for your blade wound,

37:55.360 --> 37:57.290
I can't mend that yet.

37:58.670 --> 37:59.500
I am

37:59.500 --> 38:00.940
a nameless little fox.

38:01.760 --> 38:03.820
But my little fox

38:04.110 --> 38:05.420
can't go without a name.

38:06.920 --> 38:07.940
Foxes

38:08.710 --> 38:09.820
usually go

38:10.000 --> 38:10.730
"awoo,

38:10.800 --> 38:11.980
awoo."

38:13.070 --> 38:14.820
Why don't I call you

38:15.800 --> 38:16.690
Wu?

38:18.630 --> 38:19.250
Wu!

38:21.960 --> 38:22.540
Awoo!

38:24.580 --> 38:26.100
♪One winter day♪

38:26.540 --> 38:30.700
♪By the lake, a boy in white opened his eyes♪

38:30.980 --> 38:37.220
♪He gazed at the sky, watching fate spin by...♪

38:37.440 --> 38:38.860
You don't have eyes either?

38:43.660 --> 38:49.620
♪He bowed low, gently offering wildflowers from his heart♪

38:50.260 --> 38:51.780
♪In a quiet corner♪

38:52.140 --> 38:56.300
♪Each careful stroke carried a tiny wish♪

38:56.420 --> 39:02.500
♪Lights across the shore, snow trapped his lonely heart♪

39:02.900 --> 39:09.100
♪The moon curved above, a firework lit the sky bright♪

39:09.340 --> 39:15.500
♪He looked up, counting snowflakes, waiting for spring light♪

39:15.700 --> 39:18.380
♪Tears shining in his eyes♪

39:18.460 --> 39:22.100
♪Step by step, he called and cried♪

39:22.500 --> 39:28.180
♪Yet fate fills his bowl of hope with regrets and sighs♪

39:28.460 --> 39:31.700
♪Longing drifts away like threads in the wind♪

39:31.940 --> 39:34.980
♪Like a small boat leaving the shore at night♪

39:35.340 --> 39:41.260
♪The wind takes pity and makes me turn and see♪

39:41.660 --> 39:47.300
♪Clad in golden scales, I gaze from the valley high♪

39:47.740 --> 39:53.900
♪Wiping away the dark to let the moonlight shine♪

39:54.340 --> 39:55.740
♪Through all joys and sorrows♪

39:55.900 --> 39:57.460
♪Bitter and sweet♪

39:57.660 --> 40:00.820
♪The moon stays by my side♪

40:01.260 --> 40:07.060
♪Its light is my most precious scale♪

40:14.140 --> 40:19.660
♪The moon accompanies me as I roam the mortal world♪

40:26.900 --> 40:34.420
♪She looks at me and says, you're not alone tonight♪

40:53.190 --> 40:54.020
What's wrong?

40:58.070 --> 40:58.730
What's going on?

41:01.760 --> 41:02.290
Hey, stop.

41:04.030 --> 41:05.090
It's all right.

41:13.630 --> 41:14.020
Here.

41:18.960 --> 41:19.420
Calm down.

41:19.800 --> 41:20.650
There, there.

41:22.550 --> 41:23.290
There, there.

41:25.190 --> 41:28.060
I'm in so much pain.

41:29.360 --> 41:30.980
It hurts so much.

41:33.230 --> 41:33.900
Father,

41:34.230 --> 41:35.500
Mother,

41:36.710 --> 41:38.500
take me with you.

41:39.440 --> 41:41.570
Take me with you.

41:42.070 --> 41:42.820
It's all right.

42:44.280 --> 42:44.980
You're awake.

42:45.510 --> 42:46.540
Are you all right now?

42:58.630 --> 42:59.290
What are you doing?

43:00.800 --> 43:01.820
Don't take it away!

43:03.230 --> 43:04.460
It's the only company I have!

43:04.630 --> 43:06.060
Can you give it back to me?

43:06.320 --> 43:07.730
Please give Wu back!

43:10.440 --> 43:11.290
Have you left?

43:45.030 --> 43:46.020
Eyes?

43:51.030 --> 43:52.380
You even stitched up

43:52.920 --> 43:54.060
the torn part.

44:22.190 --> 44:23.610
It's my return gift for last night.

44:26.510 --> 44:28.900
You know how to sew?

44:29.550 --> 44:30.690
My family was poor.

44:32.360 --> 44:33.900
My worn-out clothes would be passed down

44:34.480 --> 44:35.570
to my younger brother.

44:36.280 --> 44:37.460
The same piece of clothing

44:38.190 --> 44:39.770
would get patched over and over again.

44:40.670 --> 44:41.860
I did all the mending.

44:46.440 --> 44:47.210
Then why did you

44:47.960 --> 44:50.060
join the Shilin Sect?

44:51.280 --> 44:52.610
Who took care of your brother?

44:54.030 --> 44:55.290
My parents were poor,

44:56.920 --> 44:57.980
and I couldn't read either.

45:00.800 --> 45:01.690
My brother

45:03.510 --> 45:04.460
was sickly,

45:06.000 --> 45:07.690
and his treatment cost a lot of money.

45:08.880 --> 45:10.590
They said if a Shilin Sect hunter

45:10.590 --> 45:12.060
died fighting demons,

45:12.280 --> 45:13.380
the compensation

45:14.630 --> 45:16.900
would be enough to feed a poor family for ten years.

45:18.030 --> 45:19.060
So I joined.

45:20.760 --> 45:21.770
What a pity.

45:25.030 --> 45:27.130
No amount of money means

45:30.320 --> 45:31.650
anything to me now.

45:33.230 --> 45:35.420
I don't have any family left to care for now.

45:36.070 --> 45:36.570
I...

45:38.190 --> 45:40.380
I didn't mean to let your brother die.

45:41.440 --> 45:43.730
I was just an ordinary fox.

45:44.800 --> 45:46.290
I didn't know any magic at all.

45:47.510 --> 45:49.020
By the time I found you

45:49.030 --> 45:50.380
and your brother,

45:51.480 --> 45:53.070
the power Master Dragon Deity gave me

45:53.070 --> 45:54.540
had already been used up.

45:57.110 --> 45:58.650
I don't have any family either,

46:01.190 --> 46:03.940
but I know losing family

46:05.000 --> 46:06.170
must hurt terribly.

46:10.760 --> 46:12.290
How could you not have any family?

46:14.070 --> 46:14.940
Aren't foxes

46:17.030 --> 46:18.570
born in litters?

46:26.840 --> 46:27.650
Maybe

46:28.000 --> 46:30.130
it was because I was born blind.

46:31.150 --> 46:33.380
My family abandoned me in a cave

46:34.110 --> 46:35.380
and left me to fend for myself.

46:44.280 --> 46:46.020
I couldn't save your brother.

46:48.360 --> 46:50.020
How about I give you another brother?

46:54.880 --> 46:55.570
From now on,

46:57.440 --> 46:58.500
I'll be your younger brother.

47:00.100 --> 47:04.060
♪Pressing against an aching heart♪

47:04.820 --> 47:12.180
♪Through countless trials and lifetimes, each of our souls♪

47:12.580 --> 47:17.900
♪Like waves, never fearing sacrifice♪

47:50.960 --> 47:52.340
The war between humans and demons

47:52.800 --> 47:53.730
is growing worse.

47:54.360 --> 47:55.420
All beings suffer.

47:56.360 --> 47:57.610
To end this war

47:58.030 --> 47:59.380
and restore peace to the world,

48:00.230 --> 48:01.770
there is a mission certain to end in death.

48:03.480 --> 48:04.570
Are you willing to do it?

48:09.880 --> 48:10.820
If you are,

48:12.400 --> 48:13.730
swallow this dragon scale.

48:33.550 --> 48:35.340
I'm already as good as dead.

48:38.400 --> 48:39.690
Of course I'm willing.

48:57.550 --> 48:58.290
What are you doing?

49:07.000 --> 49:08.210
I owe you a life.

49:10.190 --> 49:11.210
I'm paying it back.

49:31.800 --> 49:32.650
It hurts!

49:58.420 --> 49:59.580
♪It's your light♪

49:59.780 --> 50:01.660
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

50:01.820 --> 50:04.940
♪That set the night alight♪

50:05.300 --> 50:11.820
♪And lead me through the fight♪

50:13.580 --> 50:15.460
♪Jade in the lake, sand in my hand♪

50:15.900 --> 50:20.340
♪Let bitter seeds grow, let fate bloom♪

50:21.140 --> 50:22.820
♪Face in the mirror, veiled in mist♪

50:22.980 --> 50:28.380
♪Till snow has kissed dark hair to white♪

50:29.140 --> 50:34.540
♪Night lamp burning by the old table♪

50:36.860 --> 50:42.900
♪Stitch by stitch, mending moonlight♪

50:43.860 --> 50:46.020
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

50:46.300 --> 50:51.140
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

50:51.500 --> 50:53.820
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

50:54.020 --> 50:59.100
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

50:59.340 --> 51:01.340
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

51:01.620 --> 51:05.980
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪

51:06.980 --> 51:13.940
♪Stay with me, let's gaze above♪

51:30.500 --> 51:33.460
♪Nowhere to rest, nowhere to hide♪

51:34.540 --> 51:37.940
♪Bare in body yet boundless inside♪

51:38.740 --> 51:41.260
♪Nothing to seek, nothing to erase♪

51:41.500 --> 51:44.580
♪Like water gone, like the formless moon♪

51:44.980 --> 51:47.300
♪Let every dream and wild desire♪

51:47.820 --> 51:52.220
♪Forge the edge that lifts us higher♪

51:52.460 --> 51:54.620
♪Bells through endless time, sun and moon alike in shine♪

51:55.020 --> 51:59.980
♪Love and hate all earn their crown♪

52:00.220 --> 52:01.380
♪It's your light♪

52:01.580 --> 52:03.420
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

52:03.620 --> 52:06.740
♪That set the night alight♪

52:07.500 --> 52:16.940
♪And lead me sailing afar♪
